<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFIuorno_M_J.2C_Jakubowicz_D_J.2C_Baillargeon_J_P.2C_Dillon_P.2C_Gunn_R_D.2C_Allan_G.2C_Nestler_J_E2002">Iuorno M J, Jakubowicz D J, Baillargeon J P, Dillon P, Gunn R D, Allan G, Nestler J E (2002). "Effects of d-chiro-inositol in lean women with the polycystic ovary syndrome". <i>Endocr Pract</i> <b>8</b> (6): 417–423. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15251831" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15251831">PMID 15251831</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Effects+of+d-chiro-inositol+in+lean+women+with+the+polycystic+ovary+syndrome&amp;rft.jtitle=Endocr+Pract&amp;rft.aulast=Iuorno+M+J%2C+Jakubowicz+D+J%2C+Baillargeon+J+P%2C+Dillon+P%2C+Gunn+R+D%2C+Allan+G%2C+Nestler+J+E&amp;rft.au=Iuorno+M+J%2C+Jakubowicz+D+J%2C+Baillargeon+J+P%2C+Dillon+P%2C+Gunn+R+D%2C+Allan+G%2C+Nestler+J+E&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=417%26ndash%3B423&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/15251831&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Inositol"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLarner_J2002">Larner J (2002). "D-chiro-inositol--its functional role in insulin action and its deficit in insulin resistance". <i>Int J Exp Diabetes Res</i> <b>3</b> (1): 47–60. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1080%2F15604280212528" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1080%2F15604280212528" rel="nofollow">10.1080/15604280212528</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11900279" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11900279">PMID 11900279</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=D-chiro-inositol--its+functional+role+in+insulin+action+and+its+deficit+in+insulin+resistance&amp;rft.jtitle=Int+J+Exp+Diabetes+Res&amp;rft.aulast=Larner+J&amp;rft.au=Larner+J&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.volume=3&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=47%26ndash%3B60&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1080%2F15604280212528&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/11900279&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Inositol"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
